description:
The festival-exclusive Prank Square and Midnight Prank Square are back!

This DLC contains the following:
• Prank Square *1
• Midnight Prank Square *1
• Festival Stamp Card

Clear the Festival Stamp Card requirements to get access to the following content: *2
• Mel
• Hans
• Draco
• Lizzy
• Bloompkin
• Classy Baa
• Tough Lupus
• Jack O'Lantern

*1 Prank Square and Midnight Prank Square are not available in Free Match mode.

*2 Stamp Card requirements cannot be cleared in Local Multiplayer mode.
name: 1st OBAKEIDORO! Fest Bundle
